MOST IMMEDIATE
No. 1/34/1/2008-Cab.
GOVERNMENT OF INDIA (BHARAT SARKAR)
CABINET SECRETARIAT (MANTRIMANDAL SACHIVALAYA)
New Delhi, the 11th November, 2008
20 Kartika, 1930 (S)
The undersigned is directed to say that with effect from the 11th
November, 2008:-
Shri Priyaranjan Dasmunsi relinquished the charge of the office
of the Minister of Information and Broadcasting and assumed
the charge of the office of the Minister without Portfolio; and
i)
The Prime Minister assumed the charge of the office of the
Minister of Information and Broadcasting.
ii)
The above arrangement will be in vogue during the period of
indisposition of Shri Priyaranjan Dasmunsi or till such time he is able to
resume his work as the Minister of Information and Broadcasting.
2.
(K.LSharma)
